title: Expert or Jenny's Friend: Britney the Professional Wakeboarder
description: Jenny has someone named Britney on the show that Jenny claims is a professional wakeboarder.  Dave and Steve grill Britney with questions to figure out if she is an expert in wakeboarding or if it's one of Jenny's friends pretending to be a wakeboarder.  Find out if they guess correctly!
